656
00:38:35.716 --> 00:38:38.019
<i>I think he knows about
H78, over.</i>

657
00:38:38.052 --> 00:38:39.720
[woman]
<i>I was scouting</i>

658
00:38:39.754 --> 00:38:41.421
<i>and I saw a house
